Permission: android.permission.BIND_JOB_SERVICE
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Service is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.

playstore_details.title: Fonix - Cryptocurrency Portfolio Tracker
playstore_details.description:
Fonix
‏‏Cryptocurrency Portfolio Tracker and Trading Terminal

With Fonix, Keep track of all cryptocoins, including Bitcoin, Ethereum, Litecoin, and over 1000 altcoins.
Check out the prices of the cryptocurrencies in the following fiat currencies.

Just a couple of the many great features that Fonix has to offer:

PORTFOLIO AT A GLANCE
A clear overview of your total #portfolio balance, total profit/loss since you started investing. See the trend of your cryptocurrency investments with your personal portfolio graph.

COINS OVERVIEW & WATCHLIST
See the current price, latest trend chart, your holding and your profit/loss for each coin you have in your portfolio. Or just add coins to your watchlist if you just want to keep track of certain cryptocurrencies.

CRYPTO ALERT
Set up personal notifications for each individual cryptocurrency to be ahead of the curb. We’ll also notify you when there are noteworthy evolutions happening to your portfolio.
Over 1000 Cryptocurrencies

Support for 14+ Exchanges
Coinbase, Bittrex, Bithumb, Kraken, Poloniex, Binance, Coinone, Bitfinex, and many more.
